# COMPILING

@node Compiling "Compiling BlockEd"
BlockEd has been written to compile under Aztec C V3.6a, however not all
of the include files or the library objects have been provided in the
distribution thus you should not (will not) be able to compile the program
yourself from the distribution.
@endnode

